         <abstract id="aspace_11a541fad644fa623fa06fc32bb9db82">Correspondence, diaries, journals, scrapbooks, photographs and miscellanea relating to Walter Keeler Scofield's career as naval surgeon during the Civil War and his later voyages to Europe, Asia, Africa, South America, and the West Indies.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname identifier="dts_22113da5613b53b5b83cba0b71bb6d0768c077dc" source="naf">
               <part>Scofield, Walter Keeler, 1839-1910.</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
